y well by the MFGGL formalism. The excess\nconductivity of the OPD compound, on the other hand, cannot be accounted for by\nthe MFGGL formalism with reasonable set of parameters. There is a significant\nadded contribution to {\\Delta}{\\sigma}ab(T) for the OPD sample which appears to\ncome from the presence of a PG. These findings point towards a non-pairing\norigin of the PG.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 13:43:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-09"}
